race.comment: IT'S GNARLY (4) is a gelding by Tassort on debut here for the Logan McGill yard. He's looked good with a host of jumpouts and trials. The majority of the raced brigade haven't shown a whole lot just yet so we'll side with the newcomer who looks to have some ability. DAZZLING SECRET (3) has raced three times and shown a bit. He was beaten under a length here second up off a solid return at big odds and he can continue to improve. MOUNT SABYINYO (5) was beaten five lengths on debut here but did still run second and should be better for it. Expecting a strong performance. COVERED IN CASH (2) was better second up and has each way claims.
